&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;5+ years of experience as a Business Analyst&lt;/strong&gt; delivering complex digital initiatives, with a strong track record in Agile BA roles.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Proven Mobile Expertise:&lt;/strong&gt; Hands-on exper

